data.title: Malls, Boutiques & Palmer Square
data.meta_description: Shopping in Princeton, NJ is an adventure in itself. Explore downtown for local boutiques and bookstores or head to the mall. There's something for everyone.
data.text:
Princeton-Mercer Shopping

Your shopping adventure is about to begin! Indulge in a full variety of styles and locations for shopping. While wandering the pleasant streets of downtown Princeton or the other villages of the region, check out the local bookstores, boutiques, and galleries. Princeton also boasts a variety of shopping malls, from the outlets to the upscale, close at hand or a short drive away. The Princeton-Mercer Region has it all! Shopping will give you a great opportunity to get a real sense of the incredible variety of this extraordinary region!

Whatever might be your area of shopping interest, we will guide you to the local shopping that meets your needs. Our local retailers will be pleased to welcome you to Princeton. Let them know you are a visitor experiencing the Princeton-Mercer Region and you are sure to receive a warm welcome!
